<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="row mt-4 mb-4">
  <div class="col-10 col-lg-8 offset-lg-2">
    <h2 class="mb-3">Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-muted">
      Effective date: March 5, 2026
    </p>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">1. Information We Collect</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          Wanderstay collects information you provide directly, such as username, email, securely hashed password,
          profile details, wishlist activity, reviews, and listing details submitted by hosts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">2. Automatically Collected Data</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We may collect technical data such as device/browser type, IP address, approximate location from IP,
          session identifiers, and basic usage logs used for security and performance monitoring.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">3. How We Use Information</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We use your data to create and manage accounts, display and manage listings, support wishlist and review
          features, personalize experience, prevent abuse, improve platform performance, and provide customer support.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">4. Legal Basis and Consent</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          Where required by law, we process data based on your consent, contract necessity, legal obligations, and
          legitimate interests such as fraud prevention and platform safety.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">5. Sharing of Data</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We do not sell your personal data. We may share limited data with service providers needed to operate the
          platform, such as hosting, image storage, analytics, mapping, email, and authentication services.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">6. Cookies and Sessions</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          Wanderstay uses cookies and session technologies to keep users signed in, remember preferences, protect
          accounts, and maintain security during browsing and listing management.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">7. Data Retention</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We retain account and transaction-related data only as long as necessary for service delivery, compliance,
          dispute resolution, and security purposes. Data may be removed or anonymized when no longer required.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">8. Data Security</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We apply reasonable technical and organizational safeguards to protect user data. No online platform can be
          guaranteed 100% secure, and we continuously improve our controls.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">9. Your Rights and Choices</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          You can review and update profile details. Depending on your location, you may request access, correction,
          deletion, portability, or restriction of your personal data through our support channels.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">10. Children&apos;s Privacy</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          Wanderstay is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from
          children under 13, and such information will be removed if identified.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">11. International Data Transfers</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          If data is processed outside your country, we take reasonable steps to ensure protections consistent with
          this policy and applicable legal requirements.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">12. Policy Updates</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Material changes will be reflected by updating the
          effective date on this page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">13. Contact</h5>
        <p class="card-text mb-0">
          For privacy questions or requests, please visit our <a href="/help-center">Help Center</a> page.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

